(9, 'IIT JEE', 'best iit jee coaching in indore', 'best-iit-jee-coaching-in-indore', 'Joint Entrance Examination (JEE) is an engineering entrance examination for admission to undergraduate Engineering & Architecture courses for various engineering colleges in NITs, IITs & GFTIs, India.\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ', '<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong>IIT</strong> stands for the Indian Institutes of Technology was started in 1951. In its initial years (1951-1954), students were allowed based on their academic results followed by an Interview in various centers across the country.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">It is an autonomous public academic organization with 23 campuses all over India. The IITs is a successful visionary venture of India&#39;s first Prime Minister, Nehru. The functioning of all the IITs is managed by the Institutes of Technology Act, 1961 where the Indian president is the most powerful dignitary within the management of IIT.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">Eligibility Criteria:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">Candidates appearing in (10+2) or equivalent qualifying examination, must secure a minimum of 60%(55% for SC/ST and PD) marks in aggregate in their respective Board Examination. A student can have only two attempts to write down the JEE in the year during which he or she passes the XIIth standard examination and/or in the following year.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">The student should be less than 25 years in age, with five-year relaxation for SC, ST. Candidates can appear for the exam at most two times in two consecutive years.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">IIT JEE Coaching</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">It might be difficult for some aspirants and they might find it hard to crack the exam. But you don&#39;t have to worry until Dr. IITian is here with you. If you want to fulfill your dreams and crack the JEE Mains exam in one shot, then Dr. IITian is best for you. We are</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong> </strong>the<strong> <a href=\"https://www.driitian.com/\">best IIT-JEE coaching in Indore</a></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"> offering premium courses and conducting top-notch batches for JEE Mains Preparation.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong>BEST IIT JEE Coaching in Indore</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">In our <strong>JEE Mains classes</strong>, the teachers ensure that all the concepts and topics are covered, every student&#39;s queries are solved to make sure that they are exceeding in their</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong> IIT JEE preparation</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">. We provide mock test papers with the best test series so that students don&#39;t have to face problems at the time of the exam, and ensure to provide the best revision material for the JEE Main 2020 exam.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">Our Institute provides free demo classes for IIT JEE Mains &amp; <a href=\"https://www.driitian.com/courses/best-jee-main-advanced-coaching-indore\">JEE Advanced</a> preparation. Dr. IITian&#39;s coaching environment is good for Students Where Students can quickly learn a new concept. Our experienced teachers always give attention to every student and are available 24x7 for the doubt clearance of the students.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">Dr. IItian is the <strong>Top IIT Coaching in Indore</strong>, and our expert faculty will help each &amp; every student to prepare &amp; crack the exam in a short period.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-12-26'),
(10, 'JEE Advanced', 'best jee main advanced coaching indore', 'best-jee-main-advanced-coaching-indore', 'JEE Advanced consists of topics for Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics, and Architecture Aptitude.                                                                                                                                                                                                      ', '<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong>Joint Entrance Exam&nbsp;</strong>Advanced (JEE-Advanced), is an <a href=\"https://jeeadv.ac.in/\">academic examination</a> held annually in India. It is conducted by one of the seven zonal IITs (IIT Roorkee, IIT Kharagpur, IIT Delhi, IIT Kanpur, IIT Bombay, IIT Madras, and IIT Guwahati) under the direction of the Joint Admission Board (JAB). It is the sole requirement for admission to the <strong>Indian Institutes of Technology</strong>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">Before you start with IIT JEE Preparation there are endless things to take into consideration the major one being the eligibility to appear for JEE advanced.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong>Eligibility:</strong><br />\r\nEligibility rules for appearing in JEE (Advanced) are:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">&bull; Candidates should rank amongst the highest candidates in Paper-1 of <a href=\"https://www.driitian.com/courses/best-iit-jee-coaching-in-indore\">JEE Main</a>, broken down per section.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">&bull; Candidates should be less than 25 years of age, with five-year relaxation for SC, ST, and PwD applicants.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">&bull; Candidates can attempt examination at most maximum two times in two continuous years.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">&bull; Candidates should have passed the Class XII Board Examination (or equivalent) in the previous year.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">&bull; Candidates should not have taken admission in any of the IIT earlier.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">The upcoming date for JEE 2020 exam is Sunday, May 17, 2020. Aspirants should start their JEE Advanced Preparation from now onwards as very less time is left for exams.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong>Best JEE Advanced Coaching in Indore</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">If you are here, you are looking for a <a href=\"https://www.driitian.com/blogdetail/How-To-Find-The-Best-IIT-JEE-Coaching-ClassesInstitute\">JEE Advanced coaching institute</a>, therefore Dr.itian, considered the</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong> </strong>best coaching for JEE advanced<strong>, </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">is happy to help you. We are a prominent </span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><a href=\"https://www.driitian.com/\">IIT JEE coaching institute</a><strong> </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">and</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><strong> </strong>the <strong>best JEE main advanced coaching in Indore</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">. At our institute, the teachers make sure that we work on your skills, which will help you